title: Create a Breakthrough to Break Your Comfort Zones
itunes:title: Create a Breakthrough to Break Your Comfort Zones
description:
Episode 597 - If you're going to break out of the comfort zones that keep you in place, you are going to have to create a breakthrough. Now you might say "create a breakthrough? Don't they just happen?" Well, they do but they can also be created. In this episode, I will teach you how to create those breakthroughs! If you are ready to break out of your comfort zones, join my Iron Mind 60 challenge at www.IronMind60.com
